data.description: This is the one... Beautifully updated with care and consideration for a new owner. The flooring color is everything. The perfect paint color on the walls, tech upgrades in the bathroom and exquisite tile work in the showers - this one is truly turn key. 3 bedrooms close together, with a guest bath and primary suite bathroom all on the main floor. The kitchen is spacious, has plenty of room to add more cabinets or an island to personalize for your needs. The living room has lots of natural light. In the basement, there is an incredibly spacious secondary living room with garage access. The back yard is fenced, has a GORGEOUS maple tree with lots of room for play. Make your move today! It wont last long.
